---
import AboutHeroImage from '../assets/blog-placeholder-about.jpg';
import Layout from '../layouts/BlogPost.astro';
---

<Layout
	title="About Me"
	description="A short introduction to this personal blog."
	pubDate={new Date('June 04 2026')}
	heroImage={AboutHeroImage}
>
	<p>
		Welcome. I am glad you landed here.
	</p>

	<p>
		This is a personal blog for essays, technical notes, and ideas that are worth revisiting.
		The site is intentionally simple so the writing can stay at the center.
	</p>

	<p>
		My work sits at the intersection of asset management and production-grade AI systems for
		investment workflows. I write about that middle ground: where models help, where deterministic
		engineering still matters, and what it feels like to build systems that have to work beyond a
		demo.
	</p>
</Layout>
